  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 760 380" font-family="'PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',sans-serif">
   <defs>
    <filter x="-4%" y="-4%" width="108%" height="108%">
     <fedropshadow dx="0" dy="2" stdDeviation="3" flood-opacity="0.08">
     </fedropshadow>
    </filter>
   </defs>
   <rect width="760" height="380" rx="16" fill="#FAFBFC">
   </rect>
   <text x="380" y="36" text-anchor="middle" font-size="20" font-weight="bold" fill="#1E293B">
    
    
    
    Skill ≠ 全新的东西，而是被工程化管理的 Prompt
   </text>
   <text x="380" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#94A3B8">
    
    
    
    核心未变，范式已变
   </text>
   <rect x="150" y="68" width="460" height="42" rx="10" fill="#6366F1" filter="url(#shadow)">
   </rect>
   <text x="380" y="95" text-anchor="middle" font-size="15" font-weight="bold" fill="#fff">
    
    
    
    Skill = 工程化管理 + 元数据 + 资源 + 可执行 Prompt
   </text>
   <rect x="60" y="125" width="240" height="30" rx="6" fill="#FEE2E2">
   </rect>
   <text x="180" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="bold" fill="#DC2626">
    
    
    
    Prompt
   </text>
   <rect x="340" y="125" width="50" height="30" rx="6" fill="#EEF2FF">
   </rect>
   <text x="365" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" fill="#6366F1">
    
    
    
    →
   </text>
   <rect x="430" y="125" width="240" height="30" rx="6" fill="#DCFCE7">
   </rect>
   <text x="550" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="13" font-weight="bold" fill="#16A34A">
    
    
    
    Skill
   </text>
   <rect x="680" y="125" width="60" height="30" rx="6" fill="#EEF2FF">
   </rect>
   <text x="710" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6366F1">
    
    
    
    维度
   </text>
   <rect x="60" y="165" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#FECACA" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="180" y="185" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    散落的文本片段
   </text>
   <text x="180" y="203" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    需要手动复制粘贴
   </text>
   <text x="365" y="195" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" fill="#6366F1">
    
    
    
    →
   </text>
   <rect x="430" y="165" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#BBF7D0" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="550" y="185" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    结构化文件夹
   </text>
   <text x="550" y="203" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    版本可控 · 可共享 · 可组合
   </text>
   <rect x="680" y="173" width="60" height="28" rx="6" fill="#6366F1" opacity="0.08">
   </rect>
   <text x="710" y="192" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6366F1" font-weight="bold">
    
    
    
    管理
   </text>
   <rect x="60" y="225" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#FECACA" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="180" y="245" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    每次手动注入
   </text>
   <text x="180" y="263" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    持续占用上下文窗口
   </text>
   <text x="365" y="255" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" fill="#6366F1">
    
    
    
    →
   </text>
   <rect x="430" y="225" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#BBF7D0" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="550" y="245" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    渐进式加载机制
   </text>
   <text x="550" y="263" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    元数据常驻 · 完整内容按需加载
   </text>
   <rect x="680" y="233" width="60" height="28" rx="6" fill="#6366F1" opacity="0.08">
   </rect>
   <text x="710" y="252" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6366F1" font-weight="bold">
    
    
    
    上下文
   </text>
   <rect x="60" y="285" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#FECACA" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="180" y="305" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    用户手动触发
   </text>
   <text x="180" y="323" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#991B1B">
    
    
    
    每次都要主动发起
   </text>
   <text x="365" y="315" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" fill="#6366F1">
    
    
    
    →
   </text>
   <rect x="430" y="285" width="240" height="48" rx="8" fill="#FFF" stroke="#BBF7D0" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="550" y="305" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    工具自动识别
   </text>
   <text x="550" y="323" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#166534">
    
    
    
    按需调用 · 无需人工干预
   </text>
   <rect x="680" y="293" width="60" height="28" rx="6" fill="#6366F1" opacity="0.08">
   </rect>
   <text x="710" y="312" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#6366F1" font-weight="bold">
    
    
    
    调用
   </text>
   <rect x="130" y="348" width="500" height="24" rx="8" fill="#FFF7ED" stroke="#FED7AA" stroke-width="1">
   </rect>
   <text x="380" y="365" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="#F97316" font-weight="bold">
    
    
    
    Prompt 是裸指令 · Skill 是被工具托管的可执行指令单元
   </text>
  </svg>
